name: UniversalLife_0
description: I want to use this template for my feature file

steps.name: Given  Launch Fieldnet Dev application to Enter User ID and Password click on Next 0
$("By.xpath: //h2[text()='Verify with your password']//following::input[1]") should be([exist, 10 s.])
And  click SubmitNewBusiness Menu and Enter ProducerID and click on search
And  click on Plus icon to select Environment and click on continue
When  EzApp is launched and user enters Ul Insured details state and UL product
And  User Fills UL LifeCase setup screen and NewYorkRegsixty when state is NY and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //select[@id='lb_322' or @name='lb_322']") select option containing text(Resident U.S. citizen)
And  User Fills UL Primary Insured and Primary Insured Cont screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills All UL Personal History Information screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills UL Life Product Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills UL Life Purpose of Insurance Screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills UL Life Owner and Life Owner cont screen details and click on Next
And  User fills EntityOwner and Trust Certification details Screen and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //h1[contains(text(),'Certification of Trust Agreement - Owner')]") is displayed()
$("By.xpath: //h1[contains(text(),'Certification of Trust Agreement - Owner')]") is displayed()
And  User Fills UL Life Beneficiaries and Other Coverage screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills UL Life Payment Information and Certification screen details and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Is initial premium being submitted with this Application?']//following::div[1]") is displayed()
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Premium Payor']//following::select[1]") select option containing text(Proposed Insured(s))
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Does the Premium Payor’s source of premium include a loan or premium financing?']//following::div[1]") is displayed()
And  User Fills UL HIV consent screen details and click on Next
And  User Fills UL Life Producer Statement screen details and click on Next
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Risk classification presented to client:']//following::select[1]") should be([exist, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //label[text()='Risk classification presented to client:']//following::select[1]") select option containing text(Non-Tobacco)
And  User Fills UL Life Producer Compensation screen details and click on Next
And  User Selects Additional Forms details and click on Next
And  User attaches the required docs in the Attachments Screen and click on Next
Then  Lock the Policy and do Wet or E sign as Required
